  Copyright NVIDIA Corporation and affiliates.
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

Apple Silicon adaptation work:

  Copyright 2026 AIScorpio.
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

Major adaptation areas include:

  - macOS / Apple Silicon dependency set in requirements-mac.txt
  - tokenizer backend abstraction for pandas, NumPy, scikit-learn, and mmh3
  - removal of hard runtime dependency on cuDF, CuPy, and cuML for the local path
  - Hugging Face Trainer script for local decoder training demos
  - MPS-aware decoder inference device selection
  - notebook updates for local Apple Silicon experimentation

